### ==================== 用户模块（User）接口测试 ====================
### 1. 新增教师用户
POST http://localhost:8080/user/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "teacher_li",
  "password": "123456",
  "realName": "李老师",
  "role": "TEACHER",
  "createTime": null
}

### 2. 根据ID查询用户（ID为1，对应刚才新增的用户）
GET http://localhost:8080/user/get/1

### 3. 根据用户名查询用户（登录测试）
GET http://localhost:8080/user/getByUsername/teacher_li

### 4. 查询所有教师用户
GET http://localhost:8080/user/teachers

### 5. 更新用户信息
PUT http://localhost:8080/user/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "username": "teacher_li",
  "password": "654321",
  "realName": "李老师（已修改）",
  "role": "TEACHER"
}

### 6. 删除用户
DELETE http://localhost:8080/user/delete/1